      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-1 mb-4">Best English Learning Apps for 2026: The Definitive Guide</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-500">We have tested the top English learning apps for 2026. Whether you want to master grammar, improve your pronunciation, or build vocabulary, here is the best choice for your goals.</p>
