    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Final Recommendation</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">If you are just starting, <strong>Duolingo</strong> is the best way to build a habit. Once you are ready for more depth, <strong>Babbel</strong> or <strong>Busuu</strong> will help you reach a conversational level. For those focusing on their speaking, <strong>ELSA Speak</strong> is an essential companion.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Remember that no app can replace real conversation. For live practice with human tutors, consider a platform like <a href=\"/reviews/see-guru/\" class=\"font-semibold underline\">See Guru</a> to take your skills to the next level.</p>

